### Get All
GET https://localhost:5001/api/employees

### Get By Id
GET https://localhost:5001/api/employees/1

### Create
POST https://localhost:5001/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeName": "John",
  "age": 30,
  "email": "john@email.com",
  "salary": 50000
}

### Update
PUT https://localhost:5001/api/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "employeeName": "John Updated",
  "age": 31,
  "email": "john@email.com",
  "salary": 60000
}

### Delete
DELETE https://localhost:5001/api/employees/1

